      "message": "Looking at this this morning.  I\u0027m still seeing size differences on configs I wouldn\u0027t expect to change.  Once I\u0027ve got that sorted out I\u0027ll post up the relative size changes for various configs, and then give Rec.2020+2.2 via gAMA and cHRM a try.  I do notice that the profile we\u0027re embedding is 536 bytes.",
